                    <p>2023 年 9 月份，LG 推出了 27GP95U 电竞显示器，搭载 27 英寸 NanoIPS 面板，具备 4K 分辨率 + 160Hz 刷新率，拥有 HDMI 2.1 接口，官方首发价为 3799 元。</p><p>京东焕新大促期间，叠加下方多重优惠后，仅需<span class="num"> 2818.01</span><span class="yuan"> 元包邮到手&nbsp;+ 3 期免息：</span></p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>下单立减 1200 元 + PLUS 会员立减 20.99 元。</p></li><li><p>满 2000-160 元品类券：<a href="https://union-click.jd.com/jdc?e=&amp;p=JF8BAS4JK1olXDYDZBoCUBVIMzZNXhpXVhgcDwYCXhxDXHBTTkRHA1ocDBsJVEVTbT9aXjVUUVRcEB8DV1xXDxtsbD11OUNdNic2dDwWQWpscgZ2KWJDCjskVTdgdBsBeSlyIXFYFlkqait0Yw1rXCx8PWF1JxcBf0lrWwdXfyhzKFhrMV89TiwWdw1_aDhKK392NikUdxVvc3sKbk8XKDZpLy0GakJSeQp8WyIVDXZCMhtDfz1RD2M4GFoXWQcDV19dD3sUAWgKHV8QXgEyNzkzVx1ESDNXYAklXQMyZF5eD08VBmcJE1MlXQACVVdYAEIRAWgIHmsVVQEyCBwPSQknM18LK2slXgcyV24DZkpEBGgJElsdM1tHHA0ZW04SbW8LG1sVWwQyVl9cCkknM184Kw" target="_blank">点此查看</a>。</p></li></ul><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/RqvS0Gj" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/249449/36/3753/65086/65b32095F176d20ba/f73d04d7e3f8c4b0.jpg" title="4K@160Hz + HDR600：LG 27 寸 NanoIPS 显示器 2818 元京东新低" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name"> LG 27GP95U 电竞显示器</span></span><span class="card-abstract"> HDMI 2.1、G-SYNC</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 折后 2818.01 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p>据 IT 之家此前报道，LG 最初在 27GP950 显示器上砍掉氛围灯做出了 27GP95R。新款&nbsp;27GP95U 显示器又相比&nbsp;27GP95R 取消了底座红色装饰条，其他参数相同。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="569" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/9/084becc6-56a4-48d3-a643-3984f47b635f.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="4K@160Hz + HDR600：LG 27 寸 NanoIPS 显示器 2818 元京东新低" width="1230" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="550" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/9/85426725-0f1b-462f-a6ac-498d9cb889c5.png?x-bce-process=image/fo